TRIZEN STUDIOS – FAN POLICY

You are welcome to:
• Create fan art, animations, or videos inspired by our characters
• Share them online (YouTube, X, TikTok, etc.)
• Enter fan contests

You MUST:
• Credit "Thomas Calabria / Trizen Studios"
• Include link: https://trizenstudios.netlify.app
• Label as "Fan-Made" or "Unofficial"

You CANNOT:
• Sell merch, NFTs, or monetize in any way
• Claim it's official Trizen Studios content
• Edit or reupload our original videos

Violations may result in DMCA takedown.

